cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.DS 

This paper involves the use of machine learning models (autoregressive time series forecast) and optimization techniques (Linear Quadratic Regulator, Model Predictive Control) to perform adversarial attacks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.SY (Systems and Control)
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security)
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms)
